data.description:
Nestled in prestigious Woods Creek, this home offers luxury and convenience. Enjoy a serene retreat just moments away from I-49 and Bentonville Square. Inside, discover a spacious layout with two primary suites for ultimate comfort, along with a dedicated office boasting inspiring woodland views.

Entertain effortlessly in two inviting living areas and a formal dining room. Recent updates include a new roof, modern kitchen appliances, fresh paint, new carpet, and luxury wood laminate floors.  Your outdoor living experience is enhanced by a deck and a screened-in gazebo with tranquil views of the woods.

This Woods Creek gem perfectly blends timeless charm with modernity. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and experience luxury living at its finest. Your dream home awaits!

Move In Ready and Early Occupancy Available!!!
